    This message class is for tearing down a connection.

    Send Message

    Create a new HttpTeardownMessage( connectionId, URI returnCmdChannelURI ) and specify the required connectionId and return channel. Publish this message on the HttpBaseMessage.HTTP_CMD_CHANNEL_NAME channel.

    The same HttpTeardownMessage is returned on the return channel with the following filled in.

    status - The HTTP_BRIDGE_STATUS of the call.
